{
  "stem": "7157.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So here we were in Poland, and yet our first language was German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And needless to say, this was a hated, hated language by Poland, even as early as 1939.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- we quickly tried to learn Polish and we tried to get into the-- into that language.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When you lived with your grandparents, do you recall if there was much in the way of army coming in, soldiers coming in?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was more like the police at that point.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the war hadn't really started yet officially.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as you know, they were dividing Poland into pieces at that time, so it was more like the police were-- I don't-- I wanted to say Gestapo, but quite honestly, I don't know if the Gestapo was already in effect at that point or not.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was the German police that were doing most of the-- most of the damage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, it was a time in Poland and in parts we were that you can no longer have meetings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You could no longer go to a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Certainly all the synagogues were no longer open to Jews and so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was-- it was kind of the beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could no longer escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At least that was not an avenue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For us, it didn't appear to be an avenue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we kept moving, constantly moving towards-- towards-- Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Russia.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Towards the Russian border.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, Poland was kind of divided into two pieces at that point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Half of it was Russia, the other half was Poland-- it was Germany, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Germany and Russia.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we, of course, wanted to be on the Russian side.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
